<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT19">
<l>tavañceytu nāṉmukaṉāṟ peṟṟa varattai</l>
<l>yavañceyta vāḻiyā ṉaṉṟē yuvantemmaik</l>
<l>kāppāyṉī kāppataṉai yāvāyṉī vaikunta</l>
<l>mīppāyu mevvuyirkku nī</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Are [You] not [the Lord] with a discus who rendered useless</l>
<l>The boons [that the Rākśasas] obtained from Brahmā by performing penance?</l>
<l>You are the one who gladly protects us; You are [our] protection;</l>
<l>You are the one who grants Vaikuṇṭha to all the souls!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
